# Python Agar.io game

Coded Agar.io game using sockets in Python

## Playing the game 

In order to run the game you must first run the server.py file . You can connect as many clients as you want to the server.py file

## Game 

* Each game lasts for at least 10 minutes 
* The larger you become , the slower you move .
* Each player will lose some mass at a proportional rate 

You can manipulate the code according to your wish 

## Reference 

[Sockets module](https://docs.python.org/3/library/socket.html)
[Pygame documenation](https://www.pygame.org/docs/)

I have made the project with the help of the following repo : https://github.com/techwithtim/Agar-IO
